flowchart LR
    START([用户访问]) --> LOGIN{已登录?}
    LOGIN -->|否| AUTH[登录/注册<br/>JWT认证]
    AUTH --> HOME
    LOGIN -->|是| HOME

    HOME[首页<br/>视频列表] --> SEARCH[搜索/筛选/排序]
    SEARCH --> HOME
    HOME --> DETAIL[视频详情<br/>数据/标签/B站链接]

    DETAIL --> FAV[收藏/取消]
    DETAIL --> COMMENT[评论/回复]

    HOME --> DASHBOARD[数据看板<br/>7个分析图表]
    HOME --> BIGSCREEN[可视化大屏<br/>全屏/实时时钟]
    HOME --> PROFILE[个人中心<br/>头像/密码/统计]

    DASHBOARD --> LOGOUT{退出?}
    BIGSCREEN --> LOGOUT
    PROFILE --> LOGOUT

    LOGOUT -->|是| END([返回登录页])
    LOGOUT -->|否| HOME
